      "writtenOn": "2019-05-30T13:11:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There are libraries we can use for exponential backoff instead of implementing it from scratch:\n* https://skia.googlesource.com/buildbot/+/master/android_compile/go/android_compile/checkouts.go#19\n* https://skia.googlesource.com/buildbot/+/master/go/httputils/http.go#20",
      "revId": "acd4c13e7fe86c643d295f749e134c4fb1c0047b",
